<plot>Olive rushes over to show Popeye the headline: Vaudeville is coming back. They agree to rehearse their old act. After a brief song-and-dance intro, the act begins: Popeye demonstrating his strength while Olive displays her flexibility and balance; impersonations of 'Jimmy Durante' (qv), 'Stan Laurel' (qv) and 'Groucho Marx' (qv); and the last act, more feats of strength and agility.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?449447</url></doc>
